{"tid":1563848,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「長文」思考可否效法中共統戰手段分化敵人","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T00:59:13.000Z","uid":38563,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f18e5bada924132d6c60fd053729274fdcf953","tid":1563848,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:19:59.000Z","msg":"最近同個台灣朋友傾開香港問題 同一時間都問左佢台灣情況 了解左小小點解國民黨會走親中路線 然後佢俾左條片我睇<br />\n簡單d可以用下圖總結<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SSm43gG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSSm43gG.png&h=71d942e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n詳細可以睇原片<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R336KUICMFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR336KUICMFc&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb7CEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=9b1689f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R336KUICMFc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用敵方嘅人內鬥 的確係好有效又不捐兵折將嘅手法<br />\n再加上今日見到好幾個藍絲行動 不得不作出應對<br />\n但與其花力量正面作戰 不如試下用敵人統戰手段作分化<br />\n<br />\n例如 今日你見到有班人有組織咁撕紙 我地大可以放風話係有錢收 首先分化自發撕紙嘅真心藍絲同有組織藍絲<br />\n其次放風話蛇頭收20k拆一次牆 但實際有10個人去每人只收到300咁 進一步分化有組織藍絲<br />\n最後差嘅就係一條片 內容大概就係有個藍絲揸機影住d人撕紙仲一邊大叫拆得好 最後唔覺意影到蛇頭出嚟派人工然後就話吓乜原來收錢架<br />\n<br />\n同樣道理 捉跳閘藍絲 甚至今日ifc斷正嘅100蚊唱中國國歌一樣可以用同樣手法處理 <br />\n<br />\n我唔知咁樣算唔算大家所否定嘅散播fake news行為<br />\n而我自己亦都無咁嘅人力物力去實行<br />\n以下就交俾大家討論了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"a7c7c4b5a777796de8c733c115424e2806c35706","tid":1563848,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a5f4899425ed33532e6f403c06ca774f1d01c06b","tid":1563848,"uid":60562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"而家對家咪用緊<br />\n連登大撚把分化post"},{"pid":"581d2ce71836ace584c5b224ed4a30a674f57d24","tid":1563848,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2434257f07340653c43c9c1449fbb8a5f2d250b5","tid":1563848,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e5807ee8bcc2ab45f8cff64d7917abb2b9e0426","tid":1563848,"uid":54785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5f4899425ed33532e6f403c06ca774f1d01c06b","tid":1563848,"uid":60562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"而家對家咪用緊<br />\n連登大撚把分化post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"而家就係要搵方法以其人之道還治其人之身<br />\n<br />\n如果唔瓦解藍絲，運動好難突破"},{"pid":"f20cc84a4b621f080108979d430816732173e3a8","tid":1563848,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"但佢地盲目信權威呢點，會令佢地唔理證據"},{"pid":"f8c23605c62a35376c135f4690055808dd8bf5f5","tid":1563848,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"aabf00620e8acb2af2ea834c77918049cf4bdd55","tid":1563848,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5807ee8bcc2ab45f8cff64d7917abb2b9e0426","tid":1563848,"uid":54785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5f48